name: As a user, I check export the project type ROR with key successfully with scenario 1
fullName: JIT-Export-002-Scenario-ROR-withkey-1.As a user, I check export the project type ROR with key successfully with scenario 1

steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "user" and Comment "User for dashboard admin user"
When I add new table with Name "jitexp001" and Comment "Testing"
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolstring" Type "string" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoltext" Type "text" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolinteger" Type "integer" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolfloat" Type "float" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolenum" Type "enum_type" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoldate" Type "date" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoldatetime" Type "datetime" for Table name "jitexp001" and verify
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I add module "Admin dashboard user"
When I select multi dropdown has label "Associated users tables" with value "users"
When I press Save button popover popup
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
When I select table Name "jitexp001" in dashboard table list
When I toggle on switcher of item "List of" with table Name "jitexp001"
When I toggle on switcher of item "Detail of" with table Name "jitexp001"
When I toggle on switcher of item "Create of" with table Name "jitexp001"
When I toggle on switcher of item "Update of" with table Name "jitexp001"
When I toggle on switcher of item "Delete of" with table Name "jitexp001"
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitexp001s" from list
When I toggle on API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitexp001s"
When I toggle on API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitexp001s/:id"
When I toggle on API method "POST" with endpoint "/api/jitexp001s"
When I toggle on API method "PUT" with endpoint "/api/jitexp001s/:id"
When I toggle on API method "DELETE" with endpoint "/api/jitexp001s/:id"
When I export project source code for "Ruby on Rails (API)" with option "Included master.key"
When I wait export completely with timeout
Then I should see the exporting is passed
